Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those who absolutely refused\Nto stop pushing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On occasion, they become one with their\Npersonal convictions, transforming into karma itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These beings, who while human,\Nhave also transcended humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and continue to watch over everything\Nwith the gaze of inhuman eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, unable to resist, goes down in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Make those eyes shine brighter than a torch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The destination we are aiming for is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We squarely lose our way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of the open-mouthed netherworld
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chase the traces of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If an answer can be found now, we don't mind losing it all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The echo is still reverberating
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we do not part with that voice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the yearning stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The very best of the cave raiders: the White Whistles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Armed with Relics of the netherworld\Nthey've personally excavated,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they are each known by titles\Nthat uniquely personify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even among them, one stands unrivaled\Nin terms of physical strength:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Unmovable Sovereign, Ozen the Immovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, are the stories about how she pulled up\Na gondola with 30 people inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or how she supported a boulder\Nthat was 10 meters across, all really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are rumors, purely rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, one thing is certain: such rumors\Nhave been whispered about her for a full 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"50 years"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,50 years ago she was already a White Whistle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She truly is the Unmovable Sovereign.\NWhat an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Habo, just what Relic is it\Nthat Ozen's armed with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,White Whistles are the trump cards\Nof this here city of the pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Until their whistles return home,\Nthat information won't be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any way\Nshe'd tell them about the Vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm still nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should've gone with them\Ndespite their objections after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes down to it,\Nyou're the only one who can protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this cube here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This pattern is incredibly complex...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to be at least a grade-2 Relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in the guide to recorded Relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it's not listed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that Lyza personally bought\Nbefore it could be auctioned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who carried it here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be... the Curse-Repelling Vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're half right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Curse-Repelling Vessel."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From the depths up toward the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When living creatures that couldn't make that trip\Nwere placed inside it and carried up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they weren't affected by the strain of ascending\Nand didn't die, which is why it got the name it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's not actually right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, whatever's placed inside\Nstill gets affected by the Curse and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it starts moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to you that I came to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were stillborn, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When Lyza delivered you, you were already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, you were a real annoyance, so I shoved you\Ninside this thing, but you somehow started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I got nostalgic, and I tried putting some\Nof the meat I cook dinner with in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing got loose and ran around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, it stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually, one half of it continued to move, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long you'll last...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, both you - after you started to move\Nback then - and the meat I put in there yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,attempted to head for the center of the Abyss\Nfor some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all people might have an idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you essentially the same as that meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Master... stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The things you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time you get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, you Aubade child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story is quite interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't hurt Riko any more than you already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Any way you look at it, you're really immature, Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to hear that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy, do you have a conception of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The people around here, you see,\Ndon't really believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, do you know what it is they believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is this place - the Abyss itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely because the bottom of the netherworld\Nis unknown, and because it is feared,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it has the power to become their God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was easy to head down and return back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the value of Relics and faith in the Abyss\Nwould quite possibly be shaken to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason Aubades aren't listed in the guide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't because they haven't been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they simply must not exist, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this strength of hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My arm was creaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did I hear that you lost your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm truly glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to dispose of you\Nbefore you remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll go check on the telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd let things end in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you let us go\Neven if I have to use brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've ceased moving, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't stopping her at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't break or get any thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if a bunch of strands\Nare all packed into the same area...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're lighter than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So your sturdiness is your big appeal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. I busted the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,O-o-ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really... done it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lot tougher than the floor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much more you can take...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg... Reg will break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't an opponent I can hold back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get serious, I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're going to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just let it rip like last time,\Nthe whole Seeker Camp could burn down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Refine it... thinner... sharper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I see that you breathe and blink\Neven though you're just a mechanical doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you, too,\Nwill be probably be hunted by beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happens when this thing hits something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, incredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It blasts straight through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a weapon like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Irredeemable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're irredeemable, Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your arm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something embedded inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're called Thousand-Men Wedges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I inserted them at 120 points or so all around my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the secret to my vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For as much as you criticize me,\Nyou're quite superhuman yourself, Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I fuss over lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm old, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think he's so precious,\Nyou should've kept him locked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason he went limp all of a sudden,\Nbut that's alright, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, you'll revert back\Nto being a piece of meat, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I... didn't descend into the Abyss\Nbecause I hope to live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just a little longer is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, together with Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not with Reg... I can't bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Reg! Don't lose to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are unfit for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it fit right in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg! Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just collapse and leave Riko all alone here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko is in your hands now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that one's crying too now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen has made yet another one cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a-are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Subterranean Bandits, Ozen's cave raider squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a bunch of good-for-nothings\Nwith nowhere to call home on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They were told to stay out of it,\Nbut Marulk called them here, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with a brat who can't do anything\Nbut cry and make a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got a mechanical doll who fires his weapon\Nwithout even thinking and then faints...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,While those two didn't even\Nmake a single correct decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you acted in the most appropriate manner\Nto save your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my apprentice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As punishment for disobeying my orders,\NI'll string you up naked later, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen told us to stay hidden\Nwhile the two kiddies are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ground shook countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And this kid also started sobbing\Nand came rushing over to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-is that right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you said you wanted to test Lyza's child,\Nbut you really overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that was all... j-just some act?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't go all out, I won't get the point across, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate deceiving children, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that part about disposing of the Aubade was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had any intention of doing that, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you're too sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I hit you,\Nyou weren't breaking, so I got more and more into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The primeval creatures that inhabit the deeper parts\Nof the Abyss are far more cunning and tough than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to protect that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk, please tend to the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's able to fill his belly with human food,\Nthen human medicine should probably work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work, just feed him a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lesson is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some tidying up to do, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're already here now,\Nso come on and lend me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue pushing on at your current skill level,\Nyou'll just end up as poor meals or little seedbeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than that, you'll just be\Na stain on the ground or some wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, there's no guarantee you won't end up\Nlike that as I'm trying to beat you into shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. There is one thing\NI was deceiving you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That grave I spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was buried there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think I wouldn't dig it up\Nand see for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You at least need to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen... Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already kicked you twice\Nbut you still haven't learned your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unusual one you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up with it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to cover up my scars, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As your mind comes under attack\Nin the depths of the Abyss,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,gradually the effects show up physically, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't manifest immediately\Nlike the sixth layer's Curse does,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you tread the boundaries of sanity\Nas well as life and death each time you descend,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the skin on your head is bound to get all twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just good at arranging my hair\Nto fool everyone, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't watch what you say, I'll kick you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those scars are proof of your fortitude\Nin continuing to challenge the netherworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,even as it tried to break your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen the Immovable. A genuine White Whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, will you be my mentor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen. Look, Ozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already a Black Whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, I'll catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve to say that\Nconsidering you cried when I hit you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, then. If that's the case,\Nlet's just hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, the strain of the fourth layer\Nwill make you shed tears of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's something to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have it any other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen, your personality is irredeemable,\Nbut you're still the best mentor ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The next large group of cave raiders\Narrives in three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only be able to try beating you into shape until then,\Nwhether or not it proves successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere even further than the Seeker Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the outer edge of the Abyss, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Out there, there's no worry of running into other\Ncave raiders or having anyone come to your rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ideal for training, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Training...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first assignment is what I call "survival training."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the creatures are quite docile here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps because the force field's light\Ndoesn't make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, the creatures here can see in the dark,\Nso keep your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend ten days here with the equipment you've got.\NShow me you're able to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure not to go beyond that Pillar Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider that as trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to protect this girl\Nso that she doesn't return to being a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, you can't use that thing for these ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My Incinerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and use it if you want to get Riko killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you fire it, no matter how you push yourself,\Nyou always faint after around ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a full two hours until you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time, even if I punched you,\Nslapped you against the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or dunked you in water, you still didn't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try leaving a helpless child on her own\Nin the second layer for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just how she'll be torn to shreds and eaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when you really do have to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,go all out to make sure whatever it is\Ndoesn't come after you again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter your opponent or whatever lies in the vicinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when the time comes, don't hesitate or show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, your adventure will be over\Nin the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The glittering waves that float in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bundle them and build a rainbow bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous foothold, a slope we slide on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A signpost of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left hand, with my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Join it, connect us, and let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am always beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, the present, and also the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's walk along without hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pile up multicolored dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will we head toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be together with you, the world will begin to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search for flowers that bloom at the ends of the earth
